<div class="title">A Violet-Banded Quilt Of Time/Space</div>
<div class="substance">AMT & Salvia divinorum</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Green_Guest&Exact=1">Green_Guest</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Green_Guest. "A Violet-Banded Quilt Of Time/Space: An Experience with AMT & Salvia divinorum (exp15006)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Apr 9, 2003. erowid.org/exp/15006</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

